{"tid":2065830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退中國籍入境處資料直上中共？香港人身份何去何從","createTime":"2020-06-16T00:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T04:12:56.000Z","uid":256508,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb3146aec9d8a530aac3f287f8667f4b244d98a","tid":2065830,"uid":256508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:31:55.000Z","msg":"【蘋聞追Click】<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200616&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61050792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200616%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61050792&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=b24ed7d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200616%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61050792&h=70dc5c40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200616&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61050792</a><br />\n「港版國安法」殺到香港，不少港人都擔心銅鑼灣書店事件重演，擔心自己會成為下一個李波或桂民海。當年時任中國外長王毅，高調指李波「首先是中國公民」掀起一番爭議。有港人兩年前亦因而決定到入境處申請退出中國籍，甘願放棄「三粒星」，但本月初卻收到中旅社致電，指退出中國籍後須交還回鄉卡，惹來個人資料送中疑雲。有學者指反送中運動加上《國安法》陰霾，港人身份認同有重大轉變，令不少港人希望與中國割席，甚至甘願放棄港人身份，「係摧毀咗一代人」。"},{"pid":"d877b1c56e5820938c678888e64f352e50b8b974","tid":2065830,"uid":44171,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:35:40.000Z","msg":"退支國藉又想有回鄉卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8940794b837b13478d0ecf0fe06bf1d33416bf","tid":2065830,"uid":18477,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"d877b1c56e5820938c678888e64f352e50b8b974","tid":2065830,"uid":44171,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:35:40.000Z","msg":"退支國藉又想有回鄉卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:39:14.000Z","msg":"問題係資料點由入境處去咗支旅社呀<img src=\"/assets/f